attributes.value: Learn how to play "You Shook Me All Night Long" by AC/DC.

Now, lets take a look at a famous rock song! In this lesson, Dave will walk you through the song You Shook Me All Night Long by AC/DC. All of the beats and fills in this song are 8th note based. Learning this song will allow you to apply what youve learned up to this point in a musical context. Youll be playing 8th note rock beats and transitioning to new sections with 8th note based fills - just like youve been working on throughout this Learning Path! Learning this song with the transcription will be an excellent way to work on your reading skills as well!

Related Lessons: "Creep" - Radiohead, "Sweet Home Alabama" - Lynyrd Skynyrd
